Domestic Transportation

Domestic Freight and Cargo Transportation

We Deliver Domestic Freight and Cargo Transportation Solutions

Excel Cargo Logistics has the scale and scope to meet their domestic freight and cargo transportation budget and schedule requirements of the largest and smallest companies alike. Transporting goods efficiently and affordably is what we do.

It sounds simple, but commodities are constantly moving targets. That’s why we take an aggressive and proactive approach to deliver on time and on budget. Whether shipping freight and cargo across town, across the state or across the country, Excel Cargo Logistics goes where you go. 

Excel Cargo’s strategic relationships with thousands of carriers enable quicker fulfillment time and reduced supply chain costs.  Unlike asset-based providers whose main priority is reducing out of route miles,  we determine the most efficient logistics plan for your needs with the flexibility to support changing demands. Customers of Excel Cargo consistently outperform their competitors on the supply chain of service performance and cost of operation.

White-Glove Domestic Freight Forwarder

As a top domestic freight forwarder, Excel Cargo Logistics understands that providing white-glove management of domestic freight shipping is crucial to you and your business. Known for our expert handling of routine shipments, Excel Cargo also provides time-critical and custom services for freight that requires extra care or special handling while still meeting your company’s specific delivery time requirements.

Tailored Domestic Freight and Cargo Transportation Solutions

Excel Cargo Logistics is a leading provider of domestic freight and cargo transportation services, including air, ocean, ground, and rail options. We offer the scale and scope of services to meet the budget and schedule requirements of each customer.
